  <body>
    <div class='container'>
      <h1>Welcome, {{name}}!</h1>
      <p>
        Thank you for joining the ViaPrize community. We're excited to have you!
      </p>
      <h2>Here's what you can do:</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Proposer:</strong>
          Share your ideas with proper documentation. If someone likes your
          idea, they can fund it, and someone can implement your idea and add a
          submission to your proposal.</li>
        <li><strong>Funder:</strong>
          Fund proposals that you find interesting and valuable.</li>
        <li><strong>Pursuer:</strong>
          Implement the ideas proposed by others and bring them into reality.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        If you have any queries, feel free to reply to this email or join the
        discussion form. Plus Join our community on Telegram
        {{telegramLink}}
      </p>
      <div class='footer'>
        <p>Best regards,</p>
        <p>Noah Chon Lee, Founder</p>
      </div>
    </div>
